data.description: Welcome to San Clerc Estates! This 3 Bed, 2 Bath home offers a spacious fully fenced backyard providing plenty of privacy. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances along with a breakfast bar that opens up to an inviting dining & living room space. Master suite includes a screened patio perfect for enjoying your morning coffee, stretching to the sunrise, or reading & lounging. Features sidewalks, multicar driveway & an oversized side entry car garage. The roof is only two years old with HVAC being 1.5 years of age, talk about a HECK YES?! Centrally located for easy access to major interstates such as I-95 & I-295, minutes from downtown Jacksonville or Mandarin. Come see for yourself and enjoy the ride through this serene neighborhood. Back on market and ready to sell.
